Nuer: Cɛ jɔɔc rɛy warɛgakä Ji Mɛrkɛm min Nyooth ta̱a̱ Piɛny muɔ̱n kɛnɛ ta̱a̱ lathä piɛny ɛn ɣöö thiɛlɛ lath piɛny mi bi tuɔɔk rɛy we̱c Ai̱th-lan kɛ juɔk ɛ bee. 
English: The Nuer: A war between the Nuer and the Sinkhondi, which resulted in the death of thousands of Nuer.
clean_output: The Nuer: A war between the Nuer and the Sinkhondi, which resulted in the death of thousands of Nuer.

text: Cuɛ nyuur wi̱i̱ pa̱a̱m kɛl mi̱bäär nhiam wec Mi̱kka,  jɛn ɣo̱t ɛmɔ tëë guäthdɛ kärɔa kɛ wi̱i̱muɔ̱ɔ̱n in dɔ̱ŋ.
translated_text:
Nuer: Cuɛ nyuur wi̱i̱ pa̱a̱m kɛl mi̱bäär nhiam wec Mi̱kka,  jɛn ɣo̱t ɛmɔ tëë guäthdɛ kärɔa kɛ wi̱i̱muɔ̱ɔ̱n in dɔ̱ŋ. 
English: Nuer: A Nuer is a man who is married to a woman of the same ethnic group.
clean_output: Nuer: A Nuer is a man who is married to a woman of the same ethnic group.
